text: National Highway 730C, commonly referred to as NH 730C is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 30. NH-730C runs in the state of Uttar Pradesh in India. == Route == NH730C connects Bisalpur, Miranpur Katra, Fatehgarh and Bewar in the state of Uttar Pradesh. == Junctions == : Terminal near Bisalpur. : near Miranpur Katra : Terminal near Bewar. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 730C on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Uttar Pradesh
